
Description: User story

As a player 
I want to visit the game application site

As a player
I want to be able to start a new game 

As a player
I want to be displayed with the rules of the game

As a player
I want to be able to choose between rock, paper and scissor

As a player
I want to compete against a computer
And I want to see the computers choise

As a player
I want to be given the result of the match

As a player
I want to have the choise to play again